      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this fantastic find! This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained, making it a reliable and stylish choice for your next daily driver. While it shows some light signs of use consistent with its age, it drives beautifully and is ready for its next owner to enjoy!",
