    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained. The engine and transmission are solid, offering a dependable and smooth ride for its next owner. While the exterior and interior show some minor signs of regular use, such as small scratches and light upholstery wear, the car remains aesthetically pleasing and mechanically sound. It is a great choice for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that has been cared for over the years.",
