    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The engine starts reliably and runs strong, while the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, ensuring a comfortable driving experience. The interior is clean with only minor signs of regular use, and the exterior paint retains a nice shine, though you might find a few small, age-appropriate blemishes. It is a solid, dependable car that is ready for the road without any immediate major repairs needed.",
