      "description": "Presenting an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in impeccable, showroom condition, reflecting a standard of maintenance reserved for the most discerning collectors. Every surface, mechanical component, and interior detail has been preserved to an exacting degree, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original debut. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a masterpiece of engineering that transcends the typical secondary market offering. We invite serious inquiries to witness this standard of excellence firsthand.",
      "price": 48900.0,
